TAVOLO SMART WEIGHT DETECTION SYSTEM v1.0.0

Developer: Aldo Alberto Baldeon Fabian
Nickname: Codares
Project: Tavolo IoT Weight Detection System
Date: September 2025

This project implements an advanced IoT embedded system with:
- Event-Driven Architecture
- Finite State Machine
- Reactive Programming
- SOLID Design Principles
- Edge API Communication via MQTT
- Real-time Weight Monitoring

Hardware Requirements:
- ESP32 DevKit C v4
- HX711 Weight Sensor (50kg capacity)
- LCD I2C 20x4 Display
- LED Status Indicator
- Load Cell/Strain Gauge

For technical support or collaboration opportunities:
Contact: Codares Developer

